{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Mannas Deenas irr jo ne efinu tahds pree tew pa\nahtras bijufchas / ne ka weens (ka juhs dohmajat).\nTezzetajs / tahs irr aissrehju-\nfchas / un Labbunu ne redsej-\nschus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tahs irr aissahjuſchag\nitt ka Wehstu-Laiwas / itt ka\nEhrglis us Barribu skreen.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ja es dohmaju / es grib-\nbut mannu Schehloſchanu ais-\nmirst / un mannu Skummibu\npameſt/ un atſpirgtees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad es bihſtohs par wiſ-\nfahm mannahm Sahpehn / es\nſinnu/ ka tu manni par Neno-\nfeedfigu ne turrefi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo es efinu besdeeuiigs/\ncapehz gribbu es weltidarbotees?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jepſchu es ar Sneega\nUhdeni maſgatohs/ un fehkihsti-\ntu fawas Rohkas Awota.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tatschu tu manni eeſch\n(Dublu) Bedres eemehrksi/ ta\nka mannas * Drehbes mannu\nNegantibu parahdihs.\n* Eebr: Wallod: Es fawahm paſchahm\nPrehbehim negants buhſchu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo wiꞥſch ne irr tahds\nWihrs ka es/ kam es atbilddeht\nwarretu/ ka mehs kohpa warre-\ntum preeſch Teetas eet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ne tahds Starpa-Wihrs\nirr starp mums/ kas fawu Roh-\nfu us muns abbeem warretu lift.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Lat wiꞥſch fawu Ribſti\nno mannim atxeim/ un winna\nBeedeſchana lat manni ne is-\ntruhzina.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad es runnaſchu/ un\npreeſch winna ne bihſchohs/ jo es\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta X. Nodalla.\nFiabs fuhds ne zilwezigas Wahjibas un\nzeeſchanas/ ka Deews winnu itt ka\nBesdeewigu mohazi: 2. Kur wiꞥſch\nto ar fweem Grehkeem ne efu pelni\nWehle ka wiꞥſch ne bahtu dsimmis\nLuhds par Sahpu Remdeſchanu: 20.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Anna Dwehfele\nWapnikſkuti dſihwe\nmans Schehſums\nmanni japaturr / es runna\nno mannas Dwehfeles Ri\ntuma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es fazzischu us Deet\nNe pasuddina manni/ dohd ni\nSinnu / par ko tu ar manu\nteesajees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Patihk tas tew / ka\nWarras-Darbu darri/ ka tu\nwu Rohkas Darbu atmett/\napſkaidro to Besdeewigo P\ndohmu?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Irr tew meesigas Azzi\nwoj tu ta raugi / ka Zilwe\nrauga?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Irr tawas Deenas ka 3\nweku Deenas? un tawi Gaddi\nkahda Wihra Deenas?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka tu mannu Noseegum\nmekle/ un pehz manneem Gre-\nkeim waiza.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas tawa Sinna/ ka e\nbesdeeuigs ne efinu / un ka u\nweens irr/ kas no tawas Rohka\ntsglahbj.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "* Tawas Rohkasirr mat\nni fataifſſchas / un darrijſchas\nkahds es wiſsapkahte eſmu / u\ntu nu manni aprihj.\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
